summary: I am a socially involved Researcher Biobased Sciences with an inquisitive, analytic attitude, who enjoys piecing data, knowledge, and ideas together until he finds the best solution. Fields of interest: Environmental technology, system analysis, biology, sustainability,  circular economy, innovation, education, economics, and politics. I enjoy finding and making connections, between people and information.
